Polling Loop and State Machine
```
usePaymentWatcher(...)
```
executes recursive polling with timeout scheduling:
Starts only when
```
enabled && dataValue && minAmountCRC
```
Sets state to
```
waiting
```
before each probe.
Calls
```
checkPaymentReceived(...)
```
On hit: stores event, sets
```
confirmed
```
, stops polling.
On exception: stores message, sets
error
, keeps control explicit.
On cleanup: cancels loop and clears timeout.
Default interval is
```
5000ms
```
; this is configurable via
```
intervalMs
```
